sum6 :: Int -> Bool
sum6 x = f x [0..]
 where f x y = let y1 = 2^head y 
                   ys = tail y
               in if x == y1 
         then True
      else if x < y1
              then False
           else if x > y1 && x < head (tail ys)
                then False
                            else f x ys
